name: Pocket Stars
description:
"Pocket Stars" 

Bendungan Hilir, Jakarta Indonesia. 

Joyo and Tina, both of them work at the same printing company. From time to time midnight has become their best companion, a time where they can have a deep talk after over loaded work, telling jokes and sharing their favorite topics. Started as strangers, they first hello was at midnight, unintentionally they shared the same table at the Nasi Goreng stall near their office. Few years passes and midnight has become their only bus stops, untill one day one them decided to take the same bus. 

"From all of those misprinted days we live in, you are my favorite color scheme" .


*A tribute to all of the people who worked hard in the field, we know you haven't got enough sleep during deadlines, we owe you guys big time for those perfect colors we wanted. 

0:24 secs  1080X1080p 
story + musical animated drawings by Sartje.
